          &lt;p&gt;OPM does not have authority to fire employees from other agencies. Defense attorney&#39;s argued that OPM was merely asking the other agencies to terminate employees, but Judge Alsup felt that the speed at which the terminations took place made it all too apparent that this was an order.&lt;/p&gt;
